hadiths[63]{hadithnumber,text}:
5064,"abu-Khaisma Zuhair (bin Muawiya) ne Aswad bin Qais se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Jundub bin Sufiyan ( bijli ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eidul-azha manaai, aap ne Namaz padhi aur aap us (namaz ke baad khutba , dua wghaira) se farigh huey hi they ke aap ne qurbani ke janwaron ka gosht dekha jo Namaz padhey janey se pahley zabah kar diye gaey they, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne Namaz padhney se. ya ( farmaya : ( hamarey Namaz padhney se. pahley apna qurbani ka janwar zabah kar liya wo uski jagah doosra zabah karey aur jisne zabah nahi kya, wo Allah ka naam lekar zabah kare."
5065,"abu-Ahwas Salaam-bin Saleem ne Aswad bin Qais se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jundub bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eidul-azha mein Sharik hua, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abhi kuchh bhi na kya tha siwaey iske ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( eid ki) Namaz padhai. Namaz se farigh huey, salam phera ke achcha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ki bakri dekhi ke wo Namaz se pahley zabah ki ja chuki hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne qurbani namaze-eid se pahley kar li to us qurbani ki jagah dusri qurbani karey aur jisne qurbani nahi ki to wo Allah ke naam ke sath qurbani zabah kar de."
5066,abu-Awana aur ibne-Uena ne Aswad bin Qais se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur donon ne kaha : Allah ke naam par (zabah karey) jis tarah abu-Ahwas ki hadis hai.
5067,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aswad bin Qais se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Jundub bijli (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko eidul-azha ke din dekha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi, phir khutba diya aur farmaya : jisne Namaz padhney se pahley (apni qurbani ka janwar ( zabah kar diya tha, wo uski jagah doosra zabah karey aur jisne zabah nahi kya wo Allah ke naam ke sath zabah kare."
5068,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5069,"Mutarrif ne Aamir ( Shabi ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mere maamun Hazrat abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz se pahley qurbani kar di, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye gosht ki aik ( aam ( bakri hai) qurbani ki nahi. ( unhon (Hazrat abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! mere paas bakri ka aik chh maah ka bachcha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum uski qurbani kar do aur ye tumharey siwa kisi aur ke liye jaaiz nahi hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne Namaz se pahley zabah kya usne apne ( khaney ke) liye zabah kya hai aur jisne Namaz ke baad zabah kya to uski qurbani mukammal ho gaee aur us ne musalmanon ke tareeqey ko pa liya hai."
5070,"Hushaim ne Dawud se, unhon-ne ( Aamir ( Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unke maamun Hazrat abu-Burda bin-Niyaar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zabah karne se pahley qurbani ka janwar zabah kar diya aur kehney lagey : Allah ke rasool! ye wo din hai jis mein gosht se dil bhar jata hai. (aur uski chaahat baqi nahi rehti (aur maine apne bachchon, hamsaayon aur ghar walon (ko khilaaney (ke liye qurbani ka janwar jaldi zabah kar diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aur) janwar ( zabah karo. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas aik saala doodh peeti (kheeri) bakri hai. wo gosht wali 2 bakriyon se behtar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye tumhari behtreen qurbani hai (tum usi ki qurbani kar lo (aur tumharey baad kisi ki taraf se bhi aik saala bakri ki qurbani kafi nahi hogi."
5071,"ibne-abi Adi ne Dawud se, unhon-ne ( Aamir ( Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : koi shakhs bhi Namaz se pahley hargiz ( qurbani ka janwar ( zabah na kare. to mere maamun ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! ye aisa din hai jis mein gosht se dil bhar jata hai. phir Hushaim ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
5072,"Faraas ne Aamir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo hamari tarah Namaz padhey aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh karey aur hamari qurbani karey, wo Namaz padhney se pahley zabah na kare. mere maamun ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! main apne aik betey ki taraf se qurbani kar chuka hun. aap ne farmaya : ye wo ( zabiha ( hai jisey tum ne apne ghar walon (ko khula ne) ke liye jald zabah kar liya. unhon-ne kaha : mere paas aik bakri hai jo bakriyon se behtar hai aap ne farmaya : tum uski qurbani kar do wo behtreen qurbani hai."
5073,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Zubeda yami se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj ke din ham jis kaam se shuruat karengey (wo ye hai) ke ham Namaz padhengey , phir lautengey, aur qurbani karengey. jisne aisa kya, us ne hamara tariqa pa liya aur jisne (pahley ( zabah kar liya to wo gosht hai jo usney apne ghar walon ko pesh kya hai. wo kisi tarah bhi qurbani nahi hai. Hazrat abu-Burda bin-Dinar (Raziallahu anhu) (is se pahley) zabah kar chukey they unhon-ne kaha : mere paas bakri ka aik saala bachcha hai jo 2 daanti bakri 2 daanta bakrey se behtar hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum usko zabah kar do, aur tumharey baad ye kisi ki taraf se kafi na hogi."
5074,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Zubeda se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shabi se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
5075,"Mansoor ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din ke baad hamein khutba diya, phir un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
5076,"Aasim ahwal ne Shabi se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat baraa-bin-aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein qurbani ke din khutba diya aur farmaya : koi shakhs Namaz padhney se pahley qurbani na kare. aik shakhs ne kaha : mere paas aik saala doodh peeney wali (kheeri) bakri hai. jo gosht wali do bakriyon se behtar hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum uski qurbani kar do, tumharey baad aik saala bakri kisi ke liye kafi na hogi."
5077,"Muhammad-bin-Jareer ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Salma se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Hazrat abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz se pahley qurbani ka janwer zabah kar liya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iske badley mein dusri qurbani karo. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! mere paas aik saala bakri hai. Shoba ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne kaha : aur wo do daanti bakri se behtar hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey uski jagah (zabah) kar lo lekin ye tumharey baad kisi ke liye kafi na hogi."
5078,"Wahab-bin-Jareer aur abu-Aamir aqadi ne kaha : Shoba ne hamein isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ye do daanti bakri se behtar hai, ke barey mein kisi shak ka zihaar nahi kiya."
5079,"Ismail-bin-Ibrahim (ibne-Ulaih) ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din farmaya : jis shakhs ne Namaz se pahley qurbani kar li hai wo phir usey kare. to aik aadmi khada hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ye aisa din hai ke usmein gosht ki khahish hoti hai. us ne apne hamsaayon (padosiyon) ki zarurat mandi ka bhi zikr kiya. (aisa laga) jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi uski tasdeeq ki ho. us ne (mazeed) kaha : aur mere paas aik saala bakri hai wo mujhey gosht wali do bakriyon se zyada pasand hai. kya main usey zabah kar dun? kaha : aap ne usey uski ijazat de di. (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mujhey malum nahi ke aap ki di hui rukhsat us ( shakhs) ke ilawa dusron ke liye bhi hai ya nahi? (phir) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do mendhon ka rukh kiya aur unko zabah farmaya, log khadey ho kar bakriyon ke aik chhotey se rewad ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur usko aapas mein taqseem kar liya. padhi. ya kaha : uske hissey kar liye. padhi."
5080,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Ayub aur Hisham ne Muhammad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai phir khutba diya. phir aap ne hukm diya ke jisne Namaz se pahley qurbani ki hai wo dobara karey. uske baad ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5081,"Hatim-bin-vardan ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein qurbani ke din khutba diya kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gosht ki bo mehsus hui to aap ne unko zabah karne se mana kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne (namaz se pahley) zabah kiya hai wo dobara (qurbani) kare. phir (Hatim ne) un donon (ibne-Ulaih aur Hammad-bin-Zaid) ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
5082,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sirf musanna (2 daanta) janwar ki qurbani karo haan ! agar tum ko dushwar ho to aik saala dunba ya mendha zabah kar do.
5083,abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein qurbani ke din Madina mein Namaz padhai kuchh logon ne jaldi ki aur qurbani kar li. unka khayal tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani kar li hui hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke jisne aap (ke Namaz aur khutbey se farigh honey) se pahley qurbani kar li wo aik aur qurbani karein aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pahley koi shakhs qurbani na kare.
5084,Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Leis se unhon-ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se unhon-ne abu-Khair se unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein kuchh bakriyan ata kin ke wo unko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein qurbani ke liye taqseem kar dein. aakhir mein bakri ka aik saala bachcha reh gaya unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap ne farmaya : uski qurbani tum kar lo. Quteba ne ((As'haaba (ke bajaey) (alii sahaabta (aap ke sahaba main ( taqseem kar dein. (ke alfaz kahey .
5085,"Hisham dustwaai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se unhon-ne Ba'ja Johni se unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey darmyan qurbani ke kuchh janwar baantey to mujhey aik saala bheed ya bakri mili . maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! mere hissey mein aik saala bheed ya bakri aai hai aap ne farmaya : usi ki qurbani kar do."
5086,"Muawiya bin Salam ne kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha mujhey Ba'ja bin-Abdullah ne bataya ke Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon mein qurbani ke janwar taqseem kiye. usi (pichhli) hadis ke ham mana ."
5087,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 safaid rang ke badey seengon waley mendhon ki qurbani di. aap ne unhein apne hath se zabah kya bismillaah padhi aur takbeer kahi. aap ne ( qurbani ke waqt unhein lita kar) unke rukhsar par apna qadam Mubarak rakha."
5088,"Wakee ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 khoobsurat safaid rang ke badey seengon waley mendhon ki qurbani di. kaha : maine dekha ke aap unhein apne hathon se zabah kar rahe they. aur maine dekha aap ne unke rukhsar par qadam rakha hua tha (aur ( kaha : aap ne Allah ka naam liya ( bismillaah padhi (aur takbeer kahi ."
5089,Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki : kaha : mujhey Qatada ne bataya kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani di us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah. (Shoba ne) kaha : maine Qatada se puchha : kya aap ne ( khud (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha? kaha : haan.
5090,"Saeed ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ki tarah riwayat ki magar unhon-ne ye kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bismillaahi-Allahu-akbar keh rahe they."
5091,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik seengon wala mendha laney ka hukm diya jo siyaahi mein chalta ho, siyaahi mein baithta ho aur siyaahi mein dekhta ho (yani paon, pet aur aankhen siyah hon). phir aik aisa mendha qurbani ke liye laya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! chhuri la. phir farmaya ke usko patthar se tez kar ley. maine tez kar di. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhuri li, mendhey ko pakda, usko litaaya, phir zabah kartey waqt farmaya ke bismillah, aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aal ki taraf se aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ummat ki taraf se usko qabool kar, phir uski qurbani ki."
5092,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Sufiyan (bin Saeed ( se riwayat ki, kaha mujhey mere walid (Saeed bin Masruq) ne abaya bin Rifaa bin Rafe-bin-Khadeej se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham kal dushman se ladney waley hain aur hamarey paas chhuriyan nahi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jaldi kar ya hoshiyari kar jo khoon baha de aur Allah ka naam liya jaey usko kha ley, siwaey daant aur naakhun ke aur main tujh se kahunga uski wjah ye hai ke daant haddi hai aur naakhun habshiyon ki chhuriyaan hain. rawi ne kaha ke hamein maale-ghanimat mein oont aur bakriyan milin, phir unmein se aik oont bigad gaya, aik shakhs ne usko teer se maara to wo thehar gaya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un oonton mein bhi kuchh bigad jatey hain aur bhag nikaltey hain jaisey jangli janwar bhaagtey hain. phir jab koi janwar aisa ho jaey to iske sath yahi karo. (yani door se teer se nishana karo) ."
5093,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan bin Saeed bin Masruq ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abaaya bin Rifaa bin Rafe-bin-Khadeej se, unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham tahaama ke maqam zul-Hulaifa main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. to hamein ( ghaneemat mein) bakriyan aur oont hasil huey to logon ne jald bazi ki aur) unmein se kuchh janwaron ko zabah kya, unka gosht kaata aur) haandiyan chadha din. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne hukm diya aur un haandiyon ko ulat diya gaya. phir aap ne (sab ke hissey taqseem karne ke liye) das bakriyon ko aik oont ke barabar qarar diya. iske baad Yahya-bin-Saeed ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
5094,"Ismail bin Muslim aur Umar-bin Saeed ne Saeed bin Masruq se, unhon-ne Abaaya bin Rifaa bin Rafe-bin-Khadeej se, unhon-ne apne dada Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! kal ham dushman ka saamna karengey aur hamarey paas chhuriyan nahi hain, kya ham baans ke chhilkey (ya tez dhaar khapchi) se zabah kar saktey hain? aur sarey waqiey samet hadis bayan ki aur kaha : aik oont ham se bidak kar bhag nikla to ham ne is par teer chalaey yahan tak ke usko gira liya."
5095,Zayda ne Saeed bin Masruq se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis aakhir tak poori bayan ki aur is mein kaha (ham ne kaha : ( hamarey paas chhuriyan nahi hain to kya ham baanson (ki khapchiyon) se janwar zabah kar len.
5096,"Shoba ne Saeed bin Masruq se unhon-ne Abaaya bin Rifaa bin Raafe se unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha ( ham ne kaha : ( Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kal ham dushman se muqaabla karne waley hain aur hamarey paas chhuriyan nahi hain phir hadis bayan ki, albatta usmein ye nahi kaha : logon ne jald bazi ki aur unke gosht se haandiyan ubaalney lagey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein hukm diya to unhein ulat diya gaya aur unhon-ne baqi Sara qissa bayan kya."
5097,Sufiyan ne kaha : hamein Zohri ne abu Ubaid se riwayat ki kaha : main eid ke mauqe par Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha unhon-ne khutbey se pahley Namaz padhai aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya tha ke ham teen din (guzar janey (ke baad apni qurbaniyon ka gosht khaaein.
5098,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey ibne-Azhar ke Maula abu Ubaid ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eid padhi, kaha : iske baad maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutbey se pahley hamein Namaz padhai phir logon ko khutba diya aur farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum ko teen raaton se zyada apni qurbani ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai isliye ( teen raaton ke baad ye gosht ( na khaao . (un teen dinon mein kha kar aur taqseem karke khatm kar do. ("
5099,ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey Saleh aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5100,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs apni qurbani ke gosht mein se teen din ke baad) kuchh ( na khaaey ."
5101,"ibne-Juraij aur Suhak-bin-Usman donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Leis ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5102,"ibne-abi-Umar aur abd bin Humaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Salim se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is baat se) mana kya ke teen din ke baad qurbani ka gosht khaya jaey. Salim ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) teen din se uper qurbani ka gosht nahi khaatey they aur ibne-abi-Umar ne (teen din se uper ke bajaey) teen ke baad ke alfaz kahey ."
5103,"Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Waqid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen (din/raat) ke baad qurbaniyon ke gosht khaney se mana farmaya. Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr ne kaha : maine ye baat Umra (binte-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sad Ansar) ko batai Umra ne kaha : unhon-ne sach kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye kehtey huey suna hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein baadiya ke kuchh gharaney  bhook aur kamzori ke sabab) ahista-ahista chaltey huey jahan log qurbaniyon ke liye maujood they ( qurbaan gaah mein) aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : teen din tak ke liye gosht rakh lo. jo baqi bachchey (sab ka sab ( sadqa kar do. dobara jab is (qurbani) ka mauqa aaya to logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! log to apni qurbani (ki khalon) se mashkein banatey hain aur uski charbi pighlaa kar unmein sanbhaal rakhtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya matlab? unhon-ne kaha : ye (sooratehaal ham isliye bata rahe hain ke) aap ne mana farmaya tha ke teen din ke baad qurbani ka gosht (wghaira istemal na kiya jaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine to tumhen un khaana badoshon ki wjah se mana kiya tha jo us waqt ba-mushkil aa paaey they. ab (qurbani ka gosht) khaao rakho aur sadqa karo."
5104,abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen din ke baad qurbaniyon ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya tha phir iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya : khaao aur zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) banao aur rakho.
5105,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : hamein Ata ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : (pahley) ham Mina ke teen dinon se zyada apne oonton ki qurbaniyon ka gosht nahi khaatey they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ijazat de di aur farmaya : khaao aur sath ley jao (aur sadqa karo jis tarah dusri hadison mein hai.) maine Ata se kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kaha tha ke yahan tak ke ham Madina aa gaey? (Madina tak pahunchne ke aath (8) dinon tak bataur zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) istemal kartey rahe?) unhon-ne kaha : haan."
5106,"Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham teen din se zyada qurbaniyon ka gosht nahi rakhtey they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham usmein se zaade-raah (raste ka tausha) banaaein aur us se khaaein , yani teen se zyada. (dinon tak)"
5107,"Amr (bin-Dinar) ne ata se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein qurbaniyon ka gosht zaade-raah (raste ke taushe) ke taur par Madina tak sath ley jatey they."
5108,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Aala ne Jurairi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, isi ke saath Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Aala ne hadis bayan ki, hamein Saeed ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : Madina waalo ! qurbaniyon ka gosht teen (dinon/raaton) se zyada na khaatey raho. ibne- Musanna ne (sarahat se) teen din (se zyada) kaha, sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye shikayat ki ke hamarey baal bachchey aur naukar chaakar hain. aap ne farmaya : khaao aur khilaao aur rok kar rakho ya (farmaya :) zakheera karo. ibne- Musanna ne kaha : Abdul-Aala ko (un do lafzon mein) shak hai (ke aap ne rok kar rakho farmaya, ya zakheera karo farmaya)."
5109,"Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs qurbani karey to teen din ke baad uske ghar mein (is gosht mein se) koi cheez na rahe. jab agley saal (mein eid ka din) aaya to sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya ham isi tarah karein jis tarah pichhley saal kiya tha? aap ne farmaya : nahi, wo aisa saal tha ke usmein log sakht zarurat mand they, to maine chaha ke (qurbani ka gosht) unmein phail (kar har aik tak pahunch) jaey."
5110,"Ma'n-bin-Isa ne kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne abu-Zahiriya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Jubair-bin-Nufair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apne qurbani ke janwaron mein se) qurbani ka aik janwar zabah karke farmaya : Soban ! iske gosht ko durust kar lo (sath ley janey ke liye taiyaar kar lo.) phir main wo gosht aapko khilata raha yahan tak ke aap Madina tashrif ley aaey."
5111,Zaid-bin-Hubab aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
5112,"abu Mus-hir ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Hamza ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Zubaidi ne Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair-bin-Nufair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par mujh se farmaya is gosht ko) sath ley janey ke liye) durust kar lo. unhon-ne kaha : phir maine usko taiyaar kya aur aap us gosht ko tanaawul farmatey rahe yahan tak ke Madina pahunch gaey."
5113,Muhammad bin-Mubarak ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Hamza ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Hijjatul-wada mein ke alfaz nahi kahey .
5114,"abu Sanan Zarar bin Murra ne Maharib bin Disaar se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Barida se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine (pahley ( tum ko qabron ki ziyaarat se mana kya tha, ( ab ( tum ziyaarat kar liya karo aur maine (pahley ( tum ko teen din se zyada qurbani ka gosht khaney se mana kya tha, ( ab ( tumhara jab tak ke liye ji chahey qurbani ka gosht rakho aur maine tum ko mashk ke ilawa (har qism ke bartan mein) nabeez peeney se mana kya tha, ab tum har tarah ke bartanon mein piyo aur nasha aawar cheez na piyo."
5115,"Alqama bin-Marsad ne ibne-bareeda se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine pahley tumhen mana kya tha. phir ibne- Sanan ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
5116,"Yahya-bin-Yahya Tamimi, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Saeed (bin Musaiyab) se, unhon-ne abu Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez Muhammad-bin Raafe aur abd bin Humaid ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : na janwar ka pahlotha bachcha zabah karna ( wajib / jaaiz ( hai, na rajab ke shuru mein janwar qurbaan karna durust hai. ibne- Raafe ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya : Fara se murad pahlauthi ka bachcha tha, jab wo janm paata to wo usey zabah kartey they."
5117,"ibne-abi-Umar Makki ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf se hadis sunai : unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna, wo Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se hadis riwayat kar rahe they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Ashrey (zul-hijja) shuru ho jaey aur tum mein se koi shakhs qurbani karne ka irada rakhta ho wo apne baalon aur nakhunon ko na kaatey. Sufiyan se kaha gaya ke kuchh rawi us hadis ko marfuan ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) bayan nahi kartey (Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka qaul bataatey hain) , unhon-ne kaha : lekin main usko marfooan bayan karta hun."
5118,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : Sufiyan ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se marfooan riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Ashra (zul-hijja ka ( shuru ho jaey to jis shakhs ke paas qurbani ho aur wo qurbani karne ka irada rakhta ho, wo apne baal utaarey na naakhun taraashey."
5119,"Yahya bin Kasir Anbari Abu-Ghassan ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Malik-bin-Anas se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umar-bin Muslim se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum zul-hijja ka chaand dekho aur tum mein se koi shakhs qurbani ka irada rakhta ho, wo apne baalon aur nakhunon ko) na kaatey ( apne haal par rehney de."
5120,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Malik-bin-Anas se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne umr ya Amr bin Muslim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
5121,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin Amr Laisi ne Umar-bin Muslim-bin Umara bin ukaima Lesi se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ko ye kehtey huey suna : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo keh rahi thin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ke paas zabah karne ke liye koi zabiha ho to jab zul-hijja ka chaand nazar aa jaey, wo hargiz apne baal aur naakhun na kaatey, yahan tak ke qurbani kar ley ( phir baal aur naakhun kaatey .)"
5122,"Abu-Usama ne kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin Amr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Amr bin Muslim-bin Umara Lesi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : eidul-azhaa se kuchh pahley ham Hammam mein they, kuchh logon ne chooney se apne baal saaf kiye, ahal Hammam mein se kisi shakhs ne kaha : Saeed-bin-Musaiyab us kaam (eidul-azhaa ki Namaz padhney aur qurbani karne se pahley jism par se baal wghaira kaatney ya moondney ( ko makruh qarar detey hain ya us se mana kartey hain. meri Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se mulaqat hui to maine unse is baat ka zikr kya. unhon-ne kaha : bhatijey ! ye hadis bhula di gaee aur tark kar di gaee hai. (ye pabandi malhooz nahi rakhi jati waisey ( mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne ye hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. aagey Muhammad-bin Amr se Muaz ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
5123,Saeed-bin-abi-Hilal ne Amr bin Muslim Jundae se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naam liya ( phir ( un sab ki hadis ke ham mana ( hadis bayan ki.)
5124,"Marwan bin Muawiya Fazari ne kaha : hamein Mansoor bin Hayyan ne hadis bayan ki kaha : abu Tufail Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein bayan kya, kaha : main Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha aik shakhs aap ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aapko raaz daari se kya farmatey they? aap naraz huey aur kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey koi raaz nahi bataya jis ko aur logon se chhipaaya ho. albatta aap ne mujhey char baatein irshad farmai thin. us ne puchha : ameerul-momeneen ! wo kya baatein hain? unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs apne walid par laanat karey is par Allah ki laanat hai aur jo shakhs ghairullah ke naam par zabah karey is par Allah laanat karey aur jo shakhs kisi bidati ko panah de is par Allah laanat karey aur jis shakhs ne zamin (ki had bandi) ka nishan badla is par Allah laanat kare."
5125,"abu-Khalid Ahmar Sulaiman-bin-Hayyan ne Mansoor bin Hayyan se unhon-ne abu Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha : ham ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se arz ki, hamein koi aisi cheez bataiye jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raazdaari se aapko batai ho. unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey raazdaari se koi baat nahi batai jo logon se chhipaaii ho albatta maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jis shakhs ne ghair Allah ke naam par zabah kya is par Allah laanat kare. aur Allah is par laanat karey jisne kisi bid-ati ko panah di aur Allah is par laanat kare. jisne apne waalidain par laanat ki aur Allah is par laanat karey jisne (zameen ki had bandi ka ( nishan tabdeel kya."
5126,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qasim bin abi Baza ko abu Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se ye sawal kya gaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khususi taur par koi cheez aapko ata farmaai? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein koi cheez khas hamarey liye nahi batai jo aap ne tamam logon mein aam na ki ho. albatta meri us talwaar ki niyaam mein kuchh ehkaam hain. phir aap ne aik saheefa nikala jis mein likha hua tha : jo shakhs ghair Allah ke liye zabah karey is par Allah laanat karey aur jo shakhs zamin ki (had bandi ki) nishani churaaey Allah is par laanat karey aur jo shakhs apne walid par laanat karey Allah is par laanat karey, aur jo shakhs kisi bid-ati ko panah de Allah is par laanat kare."
